changer on multiple levels,

00:09:43.680 --> 00:09:45.560 align:middle line:84%
not only for the
practice of medicine,

00:09:45.560 --> 00:09:47.870 align:middle line:84%
but also for us to
really appreciate

00:09:47.870 --> 00:09:50.630 align:middle line:84%
what the human being
is beyond this material

00:09:50.630 --> 00:09:54.260 align:middle line:84%
substance, and all the energy
that supports the material

00:09:54.260 --> 00:09:56.660 align:middle line:90%
body that surrounds it.

00:09:56.660 --> 00:09:59.300 align:middle line:84%
>> I guess that's really the
biggest thing that I'm noticing

00:09:59.300 --> 00:10:01.520 align:middle line:84%
today, whereas all
these technologies are

00:10:01.520 --> 00:10:05.900 align:middle line:84%
in their infancy, is the more
we come to an understanding

00:10:05.900 --> 00:10:08.690 align:middle line:84%
of what we have to take
into account for healing,

00:10:08.690 --> 00:10:11.698 align:middle line:84%
the more we're understanding
what is a human to begin with.

00:10:11.698 --> 00:10:13.490 align:middle line:84%
And there's so many
different facets to it.

00:10:13.490 --> 00:10:17.300 align:middle line:84%
So you mention the whole
person quite a bit.

00:10:17.300 --> 00:10:19.010 align:middle line:84%
How does integrative
medicine actually

00:10:19.010 --> 00:10:21.880 align:middle line:84%
take a look at what you
would call the whole person?

00:10:21.880 --> 00:10:23.690 align:middle line:90%
>> It's getting there.

00:10:23.690 --> 00:10:26.480 align:middle line:84%
So for me, as we said
earlier, the whole person

00:10:26.480 --> 00:10:29.330 align:middle line:84%
