00:21:00.550 --> 00:21:05.110 align:middle line:84%
having thoughts, your
mind having emotions.

00:21:05.110 --> 00:21:07.660 align:middle line:84%
But it never takes you
out of the wholeness.

00:21:07.660 --> 00:21:11.080 align:middle line:84%
