00:22:03.575 --> 00:22:05.200 align:middle line:84%
and then they carried
down descriptions

00:22:05.200 --> 00:22:07.000 align:middle line:90%
and understandings.

00:22:07.000 --> 00:22:10.330 align:middle line:84%
But at the end of the day,
what I'm talking about--

00:22:10.330 --> 00:22:12.370 align:middle line:84%
and I think the ideal of
all these traditions--

00:22:12.370 --> 00:22:15.730 align:middle line:84%
is coming into the state
of wellness, which is

00:22:15.730 --> 00:22:17.770 align:middle line:90%
